152 (b) The use of raw material products described under paragraph (a) of this
153 subdivision in the manufacture of producer or consumer goods; or
154 (c) Purchasing or otherwise acquiring scrap, used, or obsolete ferrous or
155 nonferrous metals for the eventual use of the metal for the purposes described under
